snippet.title: The Night Before Snixxmas: SNIXXMAS 2
snippet.description:
The 2nd Annual Snixxmas Charity Drive is here! 
DONATE NOW AT: www.gofundme.com/Snixxmas2

Join the Glee Cast & Crew in ringing in the holiday cheer all in the name of raising money for LA's Alexandria House, in honor of Naya Rivera!

"The Night Before Snixxmas" by Telly Kousakis

Special thanks to Justin Thorne for helping to make this video possible.

- Team Snixxmas
